        <!-- About Intro -->
        <section class="about-intro">
            <div class="about-intro-content">
                <div class="about-intro-text">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded in 2010, MSD News Portal began as a small digital news startup with a big vision: to provide accurate, unbiased, and timely news to Indian audiences. What started as a team of five journalists working out of a small office in New Delhi has grown into one of India's most respected digital news platforms.</p>
                    <p>Today, we reach millions of readers across India and the diaspora with our comprehensive coverage of politics, business, sports, technology, entertainment, and local news. Our commitment to journalistic integrity and factual reporting has earned us the trust of readers across the country.</p>
                    <p>In an era of misinformation, we remain steadfast in our mission to deliver news that you can trust, stories that matter, and analysis that provides clarity in a complex world.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-intro-image">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588681664899-f142ff2dc9b1?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80" alt="MSD News Team">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Mission & Vision -->
        <section class="mission-vision">
            <div class="mission-card">
                <div class="mission-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
                </div>
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>To deliver accurate, unbiased, and timely news that empowers citizens, fosters informed debate, and strengthens democracy. We aim to be the most trusted source of news for Indian audiences, providing comprehensive coverage across all important sectors with integrity and transparency.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="vision-card">
                <div class="vision-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                </div>
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>To build India's most respected digital news platform that sets the standard for journalistic excellence in the digital age. We envision a future where every Indian has access to reliable information that helps them make informed decisions about their lives, communities, and country.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Values -->
        <section class="our-values">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">Our Core Values</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 40px; color: var(--light-text);">
                These principles guide everything we do, from the stories we choose to cover to the way we interact with our readers.
            </p>
            
            <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
